() Tj
T*
(Northbridge Regional Bank reported net income of $84.2 million for the third quarter of 2025,) Tj
T*
(up from $79.5 million in the prior quarter. Return on average equity \(ROE\) was 11.4%, compared) Tj
T*
(to 10.8% in Q2 2025. Return on average assets \(ROA\) was 1.02%, up two basis points quarter over) Tj
T*
(quarter. Total assets grew to $28.6 billion, an increase of 3.1% from the prior quarter, driven) Tj
T*
(primarily by continued growth in the commercial real estate and commercial and industrial loan) Tj
T*
(portfolios. Management remains focused on disciplined expense control while continuing to) Tj
T*
(invest in digital banking infrastructure.) Tj
